title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Sep 12 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Sep 12 2022
description:
NYT warns Dems not to believe the polls showing them ahead. AZ Senator Mark Kelly: "It's not my job" to give Biden a report card. Audio proves why John Fetterman should drop out of the PA senate race. He can't speak and is not healthy enough to do the job. Bill Roggio, senior fellow at the Foundation for Defense of Democracies, editor of the Long War Journal, and a U.S. Army veteran joins Clay and Buck with an update on Ukraine: It's not going well for the Russians. The Biden Regime wants you to keep getting shots that don't work.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
